*React abstracts the target rendering environment from the components that we implement
React Component API
React DOM API

*Diffing, Patching, Virtual DOM

*Inside the React component Javascript XML , JSX uses code mixed with HTML to render react component
Declarative React Components makes up the React page.

*ReactComponent -> *ReactRenderer -> TargetPlatform
	Component -> React Web -> Browser
	Component -> React Native -> Mobile Device
	Component -> React Desktop -> Laptop

